Imprisoner/Choran:



Imprisoner laughed, seeing Choran knocked to the ground.  He raised his sonic 
blaster, seeing Bronco coming out of the bushes, firing missiles off at him.  
He yelled as they came at him, quickly turning his weapon to aim at the 
missiles, firing off a sonic burst in an arc at them, ducking his head, 
shrapnel digging into his back.

"We surrendered you idiots!!!"
